                    {!-- ra:000000007ac554920000000000131a50 --}  <h3 class="card-title display chalk-primary">Technical Skill Development </h3>   <p class="card-text chalk-primary">Our courses are crafted to provide marginalised youth and women with the core technical skills they need to make them employable.</p>   <i class="fa fa-plus card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i> {!-- ra:000000007ac554910000000000131a50 --}
                </div>
                    
