                    <p class="card-text">KEY FEATURES:<br />
- Courses conducted in 31 centres across 14 states<br />
- Includes technical training for Room Air Conditioning, Central Air Conditioning, and Plumbing and Electrical.<br />
- Centres affiliated to National Skill Development Corporation to provide certification to trainees<br />
- Designed for end-to-end support for trainees<br />
- Curriculum and structured syllabus designed by domain experts from Voltas<br />
- On-the-job training opportunities offered to ensure hands-on capabilities<br />
- State-of-the-art training facilities<br />
- Competent faculty<br />
- Our Train the Trainer (TTT) program ensures our trainers provide the most up-to-date curriculum to our trainees <br />
- Rigorous and regular assessment<br />
- Emphasis on Safety, Soft Skills and Life Skills components<br />
- Focus on functional English, Workplace Readiness, Ethics, Values and Customer Care<br />
- 80% placement rate for trainees on course completion<br />
- Enhances social inclusion through Affirmative Action<br />
- Students topping are also awarded with tool-kits that often work as seed capital for their entrepreneurial/self employment ventures<br />
- Provide residential training centres in the interior of cities<br />
- Stakeholder engagement<br />
- Appropriate mobilisation to apt placement and post-placement support</p>
